datasets.name: 5099c69c
queryLines:
WITH unpvt AS (
  SELECT *
  FROM actuarial_app_catalog.`variable_annuity`.va_inforce
  UNPIVOT (
    FundValue
    FOR FundNum IN (Fund1, Fund2, Fund3, Fund4, Fund5, Fund6, Fund7, Fund8, Fund9, Fund10)
  )
),
fund_val_assets AS (
SELECT unpvt.* except(FundValue),
       FundValue * LargeCapEquity AS LargeCapEquity,
       FundValue * SmallCapEquity AS SmallCapEquity,
       FundValue * IntlEquity AS IntlEquity,
       FundValue * FixedIncome AS FixedIncome,
       FundValue * Money AS Money
FROM unpvt
JOIN actuarial_app_catalog.`variable_annuity`.va_fund_map
ON unpvt.FundNum = actuarial_app_catalog.`variable_annuity`.va_fund_map.FundNum
),
fund_val_all AS
(SELECT prod.*,
      fv.* except(fv.productType)
FROM fund_val_assets fv
LEFT JOIN actuarial_app_catalog.`variable_annuity`.va_products prod
ON fv.productType = prod.productType
)

SELECT *, ROUND(DATEDIFF(currentDate, issueDate) / 365.25, 0) AS Duration,
       ROUND(DATEDIFF(issueDate, birthDate) / 365.25, 0) AS IssueAge,
       ROUND(DATEDIFF(currentDate, birthDate) / 365.25, 0) AS AttainedAge
FROM fund_val_all
UNPIVOT (
  AssetValue
  FOR AssetClass IN (LargeCapEquity, SmallCapEquity, IntlEquity, FixedIncome, Money)

datasets.name: 29545b54
queryLines:
SELECT pv.*, inf.* EXCEPT (inf.recordID, inf.productType, inf.Fund1, inf.Fund2, inf.Fund3, inf.Fund4, inf.Fund5, inf.Fund6, inf.Fund7, inf.Fund8, inf.Fund9, inf.Fund10),
       prod.* EXCEPT (prod.description),
       ROUND(DATEDIFF(currentDate, issueDate) / 365.25, 0) AS Duration,
       ROUND(DATEDIFF(issueDate, birthDate) / 365.25, 0) AS IssueAge,
       ROUND(DATEDIFF(currentDate, birthDate) / 365.25, 0) AS AttainedAge
FROM actuarial_app_catalog.`variable_annuity`.va_pv_seriatim_long pv
JOIN actuarial_app_catalog.`variable_annuity`.va_inforce inf
ON pv.recordID = inf.recordID
JOIN actuarial_app_catalog.`variable_annuity`.va_products prod
ON inf.productType = prod.productType

datasets.name: 88772dbd
queryLines:
with pv_agg as (
  SELECT rwpath, sum(sumPV) as pv_payoff FROM actuarial_app_catalog.`variable_annuity`.va_pv_seriatim_long pv
  JOIN actuarial_app_catalog.`variable_annuity`.va_inforce inf
  ON pv.recordID = inf.recordID
  JOIN actuarial_app_catalog.`variable_annuity`.va_products prod
  ON inf.productType = prod.productType
  WHERE prod.productType = :product_type
  GROUP BY rwpath
)
SELECT *, rank() OVER (ORDER BY pv_payoff DESC) as rank, rank < 500 * (1- :var_pct / 100) as in_top_pct
FROM pv_agg

datasets.name: 5f0b4736
queryLines:
with pv_agg as (
  SELECT rwpath, inf.productType as productType, sum(sumPV) as pv_payoff 
  FROM actuarial_app_catalog.`variable_annuity`.va_pv_seriatim_long pv
  JOIN actuarial_app_catalog.`variable_annuity`.va_inforce inf
  ON pv.recordID = inf.recordID
  JOIN actuarial_app_catalog.`variable_annuity`.va_products prod
  ON inf.productType = prod.productType
  GROUP BY rwpath, inf.productType
),
pv_rank as (
    SELECT *, 
    rank() OVER (partition by productType ORDER BY pv_payoff DESC) as rank, 
    CASE WHEN rank < 500 * (1- 75 / 100) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as in_cte_75,
    CASE WHEN rank < 500 * (1- 90 / 100) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as in_cte_90,
    CASE WHEN rank < 500 * (1- 95 / 100) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as in_cte_95
    FROM pv_agg
)

SELECT productType, 
      round(sum(pv_payoff * in_cte_75)/124000000)*1000000 as CTE_75, 
      round(sum(pv_payoff * in_cte_90)/49000000)*1000000 as CTE_90, 
      round(sum(pv_payoff * in_cte_95)/25000000)*1000000 as CTE_95
from pv_rank
GROUP BY productType

# Projected Rider Payoffs
Rider payoff is calculated as guarantee benefits payout (death benefits and living benefit), minus rider chargers. CTE of the present value of rider payoffs are determined at a product level.
Values are rounded to the nearest million, and floored at zero.
